      <category domain="https://www.newsdeeply.com/syria/isis/">ISIS</category>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2013 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>Charles Lister</author>
      <link>https://www.newsdeeply.com/syria/community/2013/09/27/charles-lister-syrian-militant-islamists-denounce-snc-and-form-islamic-alliance</link>
      <guid>https://www.newsdeeply.com/syria/community/2013/09/27/charles-lister-syrian-militant-islamists-denounce-snc-and-form-islamic-alliance</guid>
      <description>In a video issued late on September 24, the chief political leader of Liwa al-Tawhid, Abdulaziz Salameh, speaking on behalf of 12 other Islamist militant groups in Syria, condemned the “unrepresentative” Western-backed Syrian National Coalition (SNC) and called explicitly for “an Islamic framework based on sharia [Islamic law].”.</description>
